snippet.title: Gaze At Maze Official Trailer (Steam game)
snippet.description:
Check out Gaze At Maze on Steam: Link coming soon.
Website: http://www.amaxang-games.com/2015/01/gaze-at-maze-game-purchase-full-version.html

Gaze At Maze is a 2D top-down Maze game based on the story of a weird maze world which is full of weird looking creatures, powerful bots guarding the human embryos against intruders.
